# ðŸ§Š 2. MEDALLION ARCHITECTURE (ADLS + SYNAPSE)

### **Bronze Layer (Raw Landing Zone)**  
- Stores incoming API/DB/CSV data **as-is**  
- No transformations  
- Audit columns added  

### **Silver Layer (Cleaned + Standardized)**  
- Data type corrections  
- Null handling  
- Deduplication  
- JSON flattening  
- Lookup enrichment  
- Business rule application  

### **Gold Layer (Curated Data Warehouse)**  
- Fact tables  
- Dimension tables  
- Aggregations  
- KPI views  
- BI-ready models  



